Parse CSB date

csb_date_parse.Rd

csb_date_parse is used to parse out dates into more intellgible formats

csb_date_parse(.data, var, day, month, year, delete = FALSE)

Arguments

.data

A tibble with raw CSB data
var

name of column containing date data
day

if specified, returns a named column with parsed day
month

if specified, returns a named column with parsed month
year

if specified, returns a named column with parsed year
delete

if true, deletes the original column with unparsed data

Value

csb_date_parse returns new columns with specified names containing parsed date information

Examples

csb_date_parse(january_2018, DATETIMEINIT, dayInit)
